<br>
If Congressional funding requests from NASA are met, then Prometheus will be the dream come true for those awaiting bold new changes at the agency. The enabling technologies to be investigated will have huge potential previously unrecognised. Fear of radioactive releases stymied all progress in the area. As a result, nuclear power has remained in its infancy and only beginning to emerge from the &quot;trial by fire&quot; all technologies must pass to earn public acceptance. <br>
